<HEAD>Bush Wins Backing of Italian Newspaper</HEAD>
<DATELINE>NEW YORK (AP) </DATELINE>
<TEXT>
   Il Progresso, the Italian-language newspaper, on
Monday endorsed the candidacy of George Bush for president, saying
the Republican represents ``the traditional values of Italian
Americans.''
