<HEAD>Armed Men Rob Butcher Shop</HEAD>
<DATELINE>BARI, Italy (AP) </DATELINE>
<TEXT>
   Three armed men masked by stockings forced
employees of a butcher shop into a refrigerated room, stole more
than $100,000 and fled in the owner's car Monday, a news agency
