<TEXT>
   Israeli troops shot to death three Palestinians
and swept through the occupied territories in search of suspects
during a general strike marking the anniversary of 10 months of
rebellion.
   Also Sunday, underground Palestinian leaders called for world
intervention to stop what they called Israeli repression in the
